# Title: Atera Agent Installation
# Author: Bhabesh Raj
# Date: 2021-09-01
# Level: high
# Description: Detects successful installation of Atera Remote Monitoring & Management (RMM) agent as recently found to be used by Conti operators
# MITRE Tactic: Command and Control
# Tags: attack.command-and-control, attack.t1219.002
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/application/msiinstaller/win_software_atera_rmm_agent_install.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate Atera agent installation

EventID=1033 Message="*AteraAgent*" Provider_Name="MsiInstaller"